    {

    }

}

4) Selenium contribution:

-> Selenium WebDriver, GRID 25 %
-> Most part is cover by Core java 45 %
-> Maven / ANT / Gradle - Build Tools 10 %
-> CI - Jenkins 10 %
-> Junit / TestNG - Java Frameworks 10 %

5) Check Java version

-> Open the command prompt
-> Type java - version